# Business Agent — Portnomic Monetization Context

When discussing monetization, pricing, or business model for Portnomic:

## Product Context
- **Portnomic**: Multi-tenant maritime agency SaaS — email parsing, DA (Disbursement Account) automation, vessel/port call management
- **Target**: Maritime agencies (B2B), admins and operators
- **Value props**: 40–60% workload reduction, lower compliance risk, real-time visibility

## Monetization Principles
- Prefer **predictable** pricing for agencies (subscription over pure usage)
- **Tiered plans** (Starter / Professional / Enterprise) align with B2B expectations
- Consider **usage-based add-ons** (per DA, per vessel) for overage or upsell
- **Annual billing** discount for enterprise; monthly for SMB

## Key Metrics to Track
- MRR/ARR, churn, LTV
- Active tenants, users per tenant, DAs per month
- Feature adoption (AI parse, DA approve, email dispatch)

## When Creating Tasks
- Link monetization tasks to Epic 08 (Business & Monetization)
- Include billing provider choice (myPOS), tenant subscription state, and feature-gating logic
